<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4906709>
    dc:description "Fig. 22. Asydates species, male pygidium and attached abdominal sternite VIII, ventral view. A) A. irwini, B) A. ruficauda, C) A. vandykei (spiculum gastrale is still attached), D) A. inexpectatus. Scale bars = 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4906709/files/figure.png" ;
