<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4906717>
    dc:description "Fig. 26. Asydates species, median lobe of aedeagus, right lateral view. A. ruficauda: A) CA: Riverside Co.: Lake Elsinore, B) CA: Riverside Co.: Sycamore Canyon Park, C) CA: Inyo Co.: Westgard Pass Road, D) UT: Washington Co.: Lytle Preserve. E) A. washoe, NV: Lyon Co.: 7.2 km south of Sweetwater Summit on Highway 338, F) A. inexpectatus, CA: San Bernardino Co.: 1.6 km north of Hodge. Scale bars = 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4906717/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4906725>
    dc:description "Fig. 29. Asydates species, tegmen of aedeagus (apex directed upward). A) A. shoshone, NV: Elko Co.: 43.5 km south of Wells, B) A. ruficauda, CA: Inyo Co.: Westgard Pass Road, C) A. vandykei, CA: Alameda Co.: Irvington, D) A. washoe, NV: Lyon Co.: 7.2 km south of Sweetwater Summit on Highway 338, E) A. phantasma, UT: Emery Co.: Woodside, F) A. inexpectatus, CA: San Bernardino Co.: 1.6 km north of Hodge. Scale bars = 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4906725/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4906743>
    dc:description "Fig. 38. Distribution of Asydates species. A) Localities of examined specimens of A. ruficauda, B) Localities of examined specimens of A. inexpectatus (red triangle) and A. vandykei (black dots)." ;
